anchors.description: What height can be dragged to, the unit is px
anchors.description_zh: 可以拖到什么高度，单位是px

handleDraggingOfContent.description: Whether to handle the drag event of the panel content area. If disabled, only the head area can be dragged
handleDraggingOfContent.description_zh: 是否处理面板内容区域的拖动事件。如果禁用，则只能拖动头部区域

events.name: onHeightChange
events.description: Triggered when the height changes, the animating parameter indicates whether it is in the process of animation
events.description_zh: 在高度变化时触发，动画参数指示它是否在动画过程中
